      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL SAKI (6) has placed at the last four runs, the latest finishing second (24.20) at this track. Unbeaten in two starts jumping from this box. Well placed here and can go close with a clear run. MISS SENORITA (2) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (24.31) at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Warrants plenty of respect. SUNTORY POPPY (8) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when second beaten 2.25 lengths (23.97). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Overdue and is among the main hopes. LISSY'S GEM (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.",
